Title: File System Operations

Tasks:

Implement Create, Read, Update, and Delete on files using Node.js.

Skills: Node.js fs module, sync & async methods

# Steps---

1. Initialize Node.js project:
  mkdir file-crud && cd file-crud
  npm init -y

2. Use fs module in index.js.

3. Implement:

  Create (writeFile)

  Read (readFile)

  Update (appendFile or overwrite)

  Delete (unlink)
